{"tid":2344602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【只花你兩分鐘】鄭文傑搞果個影子議會一周內已經收到過千份公眾諮詢","createTime":"2020-12-29T01:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T22:30:23.000Z","uid":382347,"like":134,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"8b7fea722bcdd0bae1e8d64baf893e09c03c4243","tid":2344602,"uid":382347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AJQapsC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAJQapsC.jpg&h=a02bb5cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n未做公眾諮詢嘅快D入黎做，兩分鐘搞掂！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkshadowparliament.com/zh/%e6%84%8f%e8%a6%8b%e6%94%b6%e9%9b%86/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkshadowparliament.com%2Fzh%2F%25e6%2584%258f%25e8%25a6%258b%25e6%2594%25b6%25e9%259b%2586%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=2223b4e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hkshadowparliament.com/zh/%e6%84%8f%e8%a6%8b%e6%94%b6%e9%9b%86/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Facebook:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKshadowparliament\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKshadowparliament&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=5425c01f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKshadowparliament</a><br />\n<strong>Twitter: </strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKShadowParl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKShadowParl&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=1e17afca\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKShadowParl</a><br />\n<strong>IG: </strong><a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkshadowparliament/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkshadowparliament%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=18deff1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkshadowparliament/</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n在極權陰霾下尋覓前路，存承民主之期盼不至覆滅，「香港影子議會」倡議的成立，正是及時獻於香港人民的聖誕禮物。而最振奮的新年回禮，正是你們的意見反饋，<strong><span class=\"red\">短短一週內已達近千份</span></strong>，在承受打壓、猜疑、孤立、冷待之下，仍感受到民眾雖低調卻熱烈的呼應。<br />\n公眾可以在官方網站取閱公眾諮詢文件作為基礎，按照指引參與問卷調查， 藉此完成公眾諮詢的程序。 如有安全考量，<strong><span class=\"red\">建議使用 VPN 瀏覽該網站：<a href=\"http://www.hkshadowparliament.com/zh/意見收集/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkshadowparliament.com%2Fzh%2F%E6%84%8F%E8%A6%8B%E6%94%B6%E9%9B%86%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx29V2ZI%2FeZCj2RMa6yNZ9LM%3D&h=916506f9\" target=\"_blank\">www.hkshadowparliament.com/zh/意見收集/</a></span></strong><br />\n你們的意見何等重要，每多一份民眾回饋，都將決定倡議的認受性和未來，都愈能保護冒險響應的人，都令政權和世界認清人民的呼聲。<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">至此已再無退路，人民更應義無反顧，自立自強自我賦權，就地實踐民主。請繼續響應倡議，遞交屬於你的意見，共同構建香港的未來。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ebc6e8a97db0f0d70ae029ad5c85fd063c117f60","tid":2344602,"uid":164837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:21:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c8b2f12f91995de1895949ca3ebcf0785ec27ac3","tid":2344602,"uid":164837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:22:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b872a70962a1ed30859e87e2963e04f8d0eb6e7","tid":2344602,"uid":164837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:22:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db554855c3d28d685baf89faf16bd4e315bc73e3","tid":2344602,"uid":164837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:24:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01154940fac33eb97f96067212c97bdf6b12680e","tid":2344602,"uid":70771,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:26:39.000Z","msg":"推，順便思考下自己理想中既議會應該係咩形式咩制度"},{"pid":"e08eec710d3b89720679f4461a790f59c760d6eb","tid":2344602,"uid":164837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:27:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b97f501cccb3b03ba0019af9e85500a81e42a1d","tid":2344602,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:29:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"87deb23